						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1262, Vikrama, Bhādrapada, śu. 10, Va[ḍḍavāra]</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1340 September 2, Saturday</hi> in the reign of the Hoysaḷa king <hi rend="bold">Vīra-Ballāḷadēvarasa (III).</hi> His <hi rend="italic">Mahāpradhāna</hi> <hi rend="bold">Īśvara-Daṇṇāyaka,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Mācheya-Daṇṇāyaka,</hi> made a gift of <hi rend="bold">Valagalakuṇṭeyahaḷḷi</hi> as a <hi rend="italic">koḍagi</hi> to <hi rend="bold">Gōpa-Gavuṇḍa,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Chavaka Bomma-Gāvuṇḍa.</hi></p>						

