<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁgaḷu 1262 vikramasaṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vatsarada bhādrapada su 10
<lb n="4"/>vadaṁdu svasti śrīmanuma
<lb n="5" break="no"/>hāpratāpacakravartti ho
<lb n="6" break="no"/>Isaṇa srīvīraballāḷadēvarasara pra
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dhānaṁ Aḷiya māceyada(ṁ)
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṇnāya(ṁ)kara kumāraru vīsvara
<lb n="9" break="no"/>daṁṇnāyakaru cavakaboṁmagāvu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁḍana maga gōpagavuṁḍaṁge koḍa
<lb n="11" break="no"/>geyāgi valagalakuṁṭeyahaḷḷiya
<lb n="12"/>gade bedalu catusīmeya
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nū Aṣṭabhōgatējasāmyava
<lb n="14" break="no"/>nu Anubhavisalu koṭṭa ko
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ḍagege Ācaṁdrārka sukhadiṁ bi
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ṭṭevu maṁgaḷa mahāśrī śrīśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
</p>

